'''Haven of the Eldar''' can refer to:

* [[Alqualondë]], the Swanhaven of the [[Teleri]] of [[Valinor]]
* [[Avallónë]], the Elven haven of [[Tol Eressëa]].
* [[Edhellond]], the [[Elves|Elven]] haven in southern [[Gondor]].
* [[Eldalondë]], a haven of [[Númenor]].
* [[Harlond (Lindon)|Harlond]] or [[Forlond]], the havens of [[Lindon]].
* The [[Havens of the Falas]] in [[Beleriand]]: [[Brithombar]] and [[Eglarest]]
* [[Grey Havens|Mithlond]], the [[Grey Havens]] of [[Eriador]].
